body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Car Deals Inc. My name is Elijah Jones. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Hello, Elijah. My name is Evelyn Thompson.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Evelyn. Can you please provide me with your date of birth in the format day, month, year?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, my date of birth is two five zero five one nine eight eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. Can you also confirm the last four digits of your phone number for verification?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, the last four digits of my phone number are seven eight nine zero.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for confirming that, Evelyn. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all. I'm feeling relieved now. Thank you for your help, Elijah.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Evelyn. I'm glad I could assist you. Have a wonderful day!
